<sect1 id="usage.user.guide">
	<title>
	get ML guide
	</title>

<para>
send the mail with 
<screen>
guide
</screen>
to elena-ctl@fml.org address.
fml sends back the guide file to the sender.
</para>

<para>
If a file named "guide" is found at $ml_home_dir, it is used as a
template.
</para>

</sect1>
